cxgb4: Use BAR2 Going To Sleep (GTS) for T5 and later.

Use BAR2 GTS for T5. If we are on T4 use the old doorbell mechanism;
otherwise ue the new BAR2 mechanism. Use BAR2 doorbells for refilling FL's.

